#

Gala Apple Salad

10 min
$8.5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

nutsdairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

saladlight mealhealthy

Description

A refreshing, crunchy salad bursting with the sweetness of Gala apples, perfect for a light meal or side dish.

Ingredients

  • gala apples: 2, diced
  • mixed greens: 4 cups
  • walnuts: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • dried cranberries: 1/3 cup
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
